OL,3,CGovernment proposes sharing personal
OL,4,Cdata to improve credit checks
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey are a step closer to
OL,7,Faccessing credit cards more easily,
OL,8,Fwith politicians set to debate changes
OL,9,Fnext week.
OL,11,FThe Government wants to create a
OL,12,Fcentralised database to allow credit
OL,13,Freference agencies (CRAs) to carry out
OL,14,Fchecks on residents who apply for
OL,15,Fcertain financial services.
