OL,3,CGovernment proposes sharing personal
OL,4,Cdata to improve credit checks
OL,6,FIt would allow limited personal data
OL,7,Fto be shared with these companies and
OL,8,Ffollows criticism from some people who
OL,9,Fare currently unable to access popular
OL,10,Fproducts such as credit cards, as they
OL,11,Flive outside the UK.
OL,13,FRing-fencing laws require finance
OL,14,Ffirms to keep their British and
OL,15,Foffshore operations separate, leading
OL,16,Fto some credit agencies struggling to
OL,17,Fverify applications in Jersey.
