OL,3,CGovernment proposes sharing personal
OL,4,Cdata to improve credit checks
OL,6,FAs it stands, automatic credit ratings
OL,7,Fmay be generated for Jersey residents,
OL,8,Fleading to lower-than-deserved scores
OL,9,Fduring online banking and mobile
OL,10,Fcredit applications, or them being
OL,11,Fscreened out entirely.
OL,13,FThese incorrect ratings can be
OL,14,Fchanged, but it requires human
OL,15,Fintervention.
