OL,3,CGovernment proposes sharing personal
OL,4,Cdata to improve credit checks
OL,6,FThe Government's latest move to
OL,7,Fstreamline the process was proposed in
OL,8,FDecember and involves tweaking an
OL,9,Fupdate to the law made in 2023, which
OL,10,Fallowed the Chief Minister to share
OL,11,Fpersonal information with CRAs so they
OL,12,Fcould undertake necessary checks.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News about the
OL,15,Fintroduction of a centralised
OL,16,Fregister, Treasury Minister Deputy
OL,17,FElaine Millar says residents will have
OL,18,Fthe opportunity to opt out of having
OL,19,Ftheir personal details listed on the
OL,20,Fdatabase.
