OL,3,CGovernment proposes sharing personal
OL,4,Cdata to improve credit checks
OL,6,FShe explains: "The only things that
OL,7,Fare going to be accessible will be
OL,8,Fnames and addresses.
OL,10,F"That's all that's there and I think
OL,11,Fthe reality is, if you're not applying
OL,12,Ffor a credit card, they (the CRAs) are
OL,13,Fnot going to be interested in looking
OL,14,Fthrough just to see who happens to
OL,15,Flive in Jersey.
