OL,3,CGovernment proposes sharing personal
OL,4,Cdata to improve credit checks
OL,6,F"We will have a period where people
OL,7,Fcan opt out of their name and address
OL,8,Fbeing provided but the consequence of
OL,9,Fthat opt out is if you subsequently
OL,10,Fapply for a credit card, you may
OL,11,Fstruggle because they won't be able to
OL,12,Fverify who you are and where you live,
OL,13,Fwhich is an important part of the
OL,14,Fissue process."
